response.overview: When a madman dubbed 'Scorpio' terrorizes San Francisco, hard-nosed cop, Harry Callahan – famous for his take-no-prisoners approach to law enforcement – is tasked with hunting down the psychopath.
response.tagline: Detective Harry Callahan. He doesn't break murder cases. He smashes them.
response.title: Dirty Harry

titles.title: Ispettore Callaghan il caso scorpio è tuo
